🚀 My Recommendation for the Remaining ARTH.OS Roadmap

At this point, you have the foundation for a world-class NBFC platform. I would build the remaining platforms in this order:

Enterprise Data Platform (Data Lake, Data Warehouse, Master Data Management, Metadata, Data Quality)
Enterprise AI Platform (AI Copilots, Predictive Models, Decision Engine, Agent Framework)
Enterprise Workflow & BPM Platform
Enterprise Integration Platform (API Gateway, Event Bus, ESB, Connectors)
Enterprise Document & Content Management
Enterprise Notification & Communication Hub
Enterprise Identity & Access Management (IAM/PAM/SSO/MFA)
Enterprise Observability & DevSecOps Platform
Executive Command Center & Digital Twin

These platforms become the shared foundation for every business module (Loans, Gold Loans, Deposits, HRMS, CRM, Collections, Treasury, Finance, Risk, and Compliance), making ARTH.OS an enterprise operating system rather than just another ERP.